    dc:description "FIGURES 1–5. Lachesilla albrookensis n. sp. (Holotype female) 1. Right forewing. 2. Right Hindwing. 3. Subgenital plate. 4. Gonapophyses and ninth sternum. 5. Right paraproct and epiproct. Figure 2 to scale of Figure 1. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3617381/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3617385>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6–9. Lachesilla concaensis n. sp. (Holotype male). 6. Right forewing. 7. Right Hindwing. 8. Phallosome, hypandrium and claspers. 9. Right paraproct and epiproct. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3617385/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3617387>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10–14. Lachesilla herediana n. sp. (Holotype female). 10. Right forewing. 11. Right Hindwing. 12. Subgenital plate. 13. Gonapophyses and ninth sternum. 14. Right paraproct and epiproct. Figure 11 to scale of Figure 10. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3617387/files/figure.png" ;
