    dc:description "FIGURES 15–21. Lachesilla odontiforceps n. sp. (Holotype male: 15–18; paratype female: 19–21). 15. Right forewing. 16. Right Hindwing. 17. Phallosome, hypandrium and claspers. 18 Right paraproct and epiproct. 19. Subgenital plate. 20. Gonapophyses and ninth sternum. 21. Left paraproct and epiproct. Figure 16 to scale of Figure 15. Scales in mm." ;
