<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3617395>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22–25. Lachesilla oriximinaensis n. sp. (Holotype male). 22. Right forewing. 23. Right Hindwing. 24. Phallosome, hypandrium and claspers. 25. Left paraproct and epiproct. Figure 23 to scale of Figure 22. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3617395/files/figure.png" ;
