<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3617397>
    dc:description "FIGURES 26–30. Lachesilla raravis n. sp. (Holotype male). 26. Front view of head. 27. Right forewing. 28. Right Hindwing. 29. Phallosome, hypandrium and claspers. 30 Left paraproct and epiproct. Figure 28 to scale of Figure 27. Scales in mm." ;
