    dc:description "FIGURES 34–40. Lachesilla tenuidenticulata n. sp. (Holotype male: 34–37; paratype female: 38–40). 34. Right forewing. 35. Right Hindwing. 36. Phallosome, hypandrium and claspers. 37. Left paraproct and epiproct. 38. Subgenital plate. 39. Gonapophyses and ninth sternum. 40. Left paraproct and epiproct. Figure 35 to scale of Figure 34. Scales in mm." ;
